Currently JIRA Subscription feature provides email reports with links to issues for a maximum of 200 results. An interesting use case we have had is "How do we get reports at midnight every Sunday capturing Snapshot from a week to week basis?". 

Email Subscription in JIRA will show you 200 results and provide a link to take you to JIRA (which is current) instead of a snapshot.

Ideally Jira should provide an option for subscription to capture the snapshot and sent as an excel spreadsheet via email with custom fields.

