[Adding a Custom Event|https://confluence.atlassian.com/display/JIRA/Adding+a+Custom+Event] has a broken link.

Under the *Configuring a post function to fire the custom event* session, number *3*:

{quote}
Navigate to workflow transition post-function screen to be edited. See Configuring Workflow and Applying Post Functions to Transitions for more information.
{quote}

The *Applying Post Functions to Transitions* points to https://confluence.atlassian.com/display/JIRA/Configuring+Workflow#ConfiguringWorkflow-postfunctions, and the post functions are no longer displayed in this documentation, but on https://confluence.atlassian.com/display/JIRA/Advanced+workflow+configuration

