Currently, when I make a custom field with options (for example of "Select List" type), I am not able to actually set the options or default value in any of the main 'create custom field' menus. 

When I am finished making the custom field (after context creation and screen placement), I am taken back to the main Custom Field page. From here I have to find the field I just made (we have 400+ in our instance) and then go through at least three more clicks before I can begin to configure the field.

I would like to be able to configure the field options and default value ideally during or after initial context creation.

